snippet.title: CLONY // Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Game ► https://store.steampowered.com/app/2953590/CLONY/

This is a 2D puzzle game with gravity. You can create a clone above your own head, and if you can press all the yellow buttons at the same time, you will clear the puzzle. Test your own puzzle skills while relaxing.

Developed by 
YUJI Lab.
